video.title: Marvel's Jessica Jones
video.synopsis: Haunted by a traumatic past, Jessica Jones uses her gifts as a private eye to find her tormentor before he can harm anyone else in Hell's Kitchen.

episodes.synopsis: Jessica Jones is hired to find a pretty NYU student who's vanished, but it turns out to be more than a simple missing persons case.
episodes.title: AKA Ladies Night

episodes.synopsis: Jessica vows to prove Hope's innocence, even though it means tracking down a terrifying figure from her own past.
episodes.title: AKA Crush Syndrome

episodes.synopsis: It won't be easy to acquire or deploy, but Jessica thinks she's found a weapon to use against Kilgrave. Luke and Jessica bond over their similarities.
episodes.title: AKA It's Called Whiskey

episodes.synopsis: A new case demands attention as Jessica tries to find out who's spying on her for Kilgrave. Trish's radio show yields unexpected consequences.
episodes.title: AKA 99 Friends

episodes.synopsis: Despite Jessica's objections, Trish's new friend Simpson gets involved in the hunt for Kilgrave. Jessica recalls a pivotal moment in her life.
episodes.title: AKA The Sandwich Saved Me

episodes.synopsis: Luke hires Jessica to help him find someone who may have skipped town, but she fears he'll learn too much about her history in the process.
episodes.title: AKA You're a Winner!

episodes.synopsis: Malcolm, Simpson and Trish go rogue to prevent Jessica from carrying out an extreme plan to outwit Kilgrave.
episodes.title: AKA Top Shelf Perverts

episodes.synopsis: Jessica experiences a strange homecoming courtesy of Kilgrave. Hogarth's conflict with her estranged wife reaches a tipping point.
episodes.title: AKA WWJD?

episodes.synopsis: Just when Jessica has Kilgrave where she wants him, Hogarth's involvement complicates the situation. Details of Kilgrave's past emerge.
episodes.title: AKA Sin Bin

episodes.synopsis: A discovery has the potential to change the entire game -- if Jessica can refuse Kilgrave's offer.
episodes.title: AKA 1,000 Cuts

episodes.synopsis: Jessica searches the morgues for clues. Trish goes all out to keep Simpson from getting in Jessica's way. Malcolm has an epiphany.
episodes.title: AKA I've Got the Blues

episodes.synopsis: The hunt for Kilgrave reunites Jessica with Luke. Trish receives some unexpected information about Simpson and Jessica.
episodes.title: AKA Take a Bloody Number

episodes.synopsis: Jessica and Luke get help from someone else in the neighborhood. Kilgrave gears up for a major test of his powers against Jessica.
episodes.title: AKA Smile

episodes.synopsis: While Jessica deals with a rival PI and a paranoid would-be client, Trish digs up a medical file that could unlock the mystery of Jessica's powers.
episodes.title: AKA Start at the Beginning

episodes.synopsis: Jessica sets out to find Dr. Kozlov and makes a startling discovery. Trish recruits Malcolm for backup as she visits a figure from her past.
episodes.title: AKA Freak Accident

episodes.synopsis: As her visions intensify, Jessica visits an abandoned clinic, where she stumbles on a new lead. Jeri faces an ultimatum after her secret gets out.
episodes.title: AKA Sole Survivor

episodes.synopsis: Between anger management classes and tabloid scandals, Jessica and Trish track down a third patient linked to IGH. Oscar extends an olive branch.
episodes.title: AKA God Help the Hobo

episodes.synopsis: Backed into a corner, Jessica's forced to share her intel on the killer. A groggy Trish tries to pull herself together before an important meeting.
episodes.title: AKA The Octopus

episodes.synopsis: Jessica gate-crashes an exclusive country club on the hunt for the killer, and Trish's new addiction begins to spiral out of control.
episodes.title: AKA Facetime

episodes.synopsis: Flashbacks shed new light on the aftermath of the family's car accident and reveal a painful turning point in Jessica's adult life.
episodes.title: AKA I Want Your Cray Cray

episodes.synopsis: While Jessica debates her next move, Malcolm confronts Trish about her erratic behavior, and Jeri makes contact with a healer.
episodes.title: AKA Ain’t We Got Fun

episodes.synopsis: The shooting forces Jessica to rethink her plans. Meanwhile, Oscar asks for help with a family crisis, and Trish’s frustrations finally boil over.
episodes.title: AKA Shark in the Bathtub, Monster in the Bed

episodes.synopsis: Jeri finagles a deal for her new client in exchange for Karl’s location. Trish forges ahead with her own investigation. A prison guard crosses a line.
episodes.title: AKA Pork Chop

episodes.synopsis: Shocked by her own actions and haunted by visions of Kilgrave, Jessica worries she’s turning into a monster. Trish's plans for Karl become clear.
episodes.title: AKA Three Lives and Counting

episodes.synopsis: As Jessica and Dorothy wait anxiously for updates on Trish, a call from Costa brings alarming news. Jeri hatches a plan to get her revenge.
episodes.title: AKA Pray for My Patsy

episodes.synopsis: Waking up in unfamiliar surroundings, Jessica once again finds herself torn between two worlds and facing an impossible choice.
episodes.title: AKA Playland

episodes.synopsis: As Jessica focuses on helping the helpless, Dorothy Walker shows up at Alias to beg for help finding a missing Trish.
episodes.title: A.K.A The Perfect Burger

episodes.synopsis: Tensions run high between Jessica and Trish as Trish hones her new catlike skills and scours the city for a chance to be a hero.
episodes.title: A.K.A You're Welcome

episodes.synopsis: Itching to get back out on the streets and find her attacker, Jessica defies her doctor's advice. Jeri reconnects with her college flame Kith.
episodes.title: A.K.A I Have No Spleen

episodes.synopsis: Jessica learns there's more to Erik than meets the eye as they track down three potential attackers. Malcolm digs up dirt on Kith's husband.
episodes.title: A.K.A Customer Service is Standing By

episodes.synopsis: Teaming up with Trish to stake out Sallinger, Jessica makes a startling discovery. Jeri's plot to expose Peter yields unexpected consequences.
episodes.title: A.K.A I Wish

episodes.synopsis: As the police sift through the gruesome crime scene, Jessica and Trish race to find Sallinger’s latest captive.
episodes.title: A.K.A Sorry Face

episodes.synopsis: Jessica and Trish go on a road trip to dig into Sallinger's past and unearth a horrifying discovery.
episodes.title: A.K.A The Double Half-Wappinger

episodes.synopsis: When Sallinger posts a video teasing his next crime, Jessica responds with her own media play. Jeri demands that Malcolm identify the masked woman.
episodes.title: A.K.A Camera Friendly

episodes.synopsis: After a shocking blow, Jessica's forced to choose between protecting Trish and destroying Sallinger. Jeri seizes a chance to get back in Kith's life.
episodes.title: A.K.A I Did Something Today

episodes.synopsis: Jessica wrestles with her emotions as she tries to untangle herself from a murder investigation.
episodes.title: A.K.A Hero Pants

episodes.synopsis: Trish revisits her troubled childhood with Dorothy while plotting to stop Sallinger and stamp out evil across the city.
episodes.title: A.K.A Hellcat

episodes.synopsis: As Trish makes a move on Sallinger, Jessica intervenes -- and ends up caught in a harrowing dance with the killer.
episodes.title: A.K.A A Lotta Worms

episodes.synopsis: An old friend visits Jessica as she sets out on an agonizing mission and learns the true cost of being a hero.
episodes.title: A.K.A Everything
